://dogtime.com/lifestyle/4382-low-energy-couch-potato-dogs-list">relaxing at home</a>, having a big dog by your side can provide an extra layer of companionship and security, making them an ideal choice for those seeking a devoted and protective four-legged friend.</p>\n<p>Check out our guides to <a href="https://dogtime.com/lifestyle/21883-huge-dog-breeds">huge dog breeds that give you more to love</a>. Also, read up on the <a href="https://dogtime.com/reference/110601-biggest-dog-breeds-in-the-world">biggest dog breeds in the world</a>!</p>\n</div>', 1, 'GettyImages-912145654-e168705067.png', 1, 'jon-stewart-announces-death-of-family-dog-on-the-daily-show-'),
